name: Wooden Birdcage Necklace
description:
Adorable laser-cut wooden birdcage necklace, natural finish with the lovely effect of burnt edges.

The birdcage charm measures approx 5.5cm H x 3.2cm W and is attached to a 75cm gold plated chain

Each necklace comes with a 100% cotton Mabel Made This pouch.

name: Personalised Initial Necklace, Made to Order
description:
Lovely initial necklace, handmade to order for you by Mabel Made This

Each necklace will be made using one letter charm of your choice and a 16 or 18 inch chunky 4mm gold plated curb chain. The letter charms are approx. 10mmW x 15mmL and are in the font as shown. Let me know if you want to see what your letter would look like before you purchase and I will gladly email you a picture.

When placing your order, simply chose your letter and length of chain. As these are made to order please allow up to 1 week production time from the date of purchase, if you need something urgently please convo me and I will try my best to get your necklace to you sooner!

Each necklace comes with a 100% cotton Mabel Made This pouch.

Looking for a necklace with your whole name or favourite word?
Mabel Made This also custom makes name necklaces of 2+ letters, please take a look at the rest of my shop for more options!

© Copyright Mabel Made This 2013, All Rights Reserved

All photography by my talented friend Levi Miller

name: Personalised Initial/Name Necklace, Made to Order, 1 - 3 LETTERS

Each necklace will be made using up to 3 letter charms of your choice and a 16 or 18 inch chunky 4mm gold plated curb chain. The letter charms are approx. 10mmW x 15mmL and are in the font as shown. Let me know if you want to see what your letters would look like before you purchase and I will gladly email you a picture

When placing your order, simply chose your size of chain and please add instructions for which letters you would like in the 'notes to seller' box. name: Lily Russian Doll Necklace
description:

N.B There is only one of each of these russian doll necklaces
